# Clara visual design

**Direction:** **Grove green** leads (**`#5F6F52`**), **orange** is a warm accent (**`#C2782E`**). **Warm plaster surfaces** on a **sage-tinted** page (**`#F5F1E8`**). Typography: **Inter** for UI and SR line; **Fraunces** for headings and wordmark “Clara”.

## Tokens (`tailwind.config.ts` → `clara-*`)

| Token | Hex | Role |
|-------|-----|------|
| `bg` | `#F5F1E8` | Page / app background |
| `surface` | `#FDFBF7` | Cards, panels, inputs |
| `tint` | `#EFE8DC` | Soft wash (metrics, progress track, sidebar fade) |
| `border` | `#E0D8CC` | Dividers, outlines |
| `deep` | `#2C2824` | Body text, labels |
| `muted` | `#7A756E` | Secondary labels |
| `primary` | `#5F6F52` | Default buttons, active nav emphasis, solid green badges, wordmark “Clara” |
| `primary-dark` | `#4D5C42` | Primary hover |
| `accent` | `#C2782E` | **Headings** (`h1`–`h6`, TopBar title), links, focus rings on primary, warm highlights |
| `accent-soft` | `#F3EBE0` | Warm badge background |
| `accent-foreground` | `#8B5220` | Text on warm badges |
| `sea` | `#2C5F63` | Prose links |
| `sea-muted` | `#3D7377` | Prose link hover |
| `leaf` | `#5F6F52` | Success (same as primary) |

## Badges (`Badge.tsx`)

- **green** — primary: green fill, white text.
- **yellow** — warm: `accent-soft` + `accent` text + light ring.
- **red** — dark label: `deep` + white text.
- **blue** — soft: `tint` + `primary` text (info / neutral emphasis).
- **grey** — outlined surface.

## Buttons

- **Primary:** `bg-clara-primary`, `hover:bg-clara-primary-dark`, white text; focus outline `clara-accent`.
- **Destructive:** `bg-clara-deep`, white text.

## Layout

- **Sidebar:** `from-clara-bg` → `to-clara-tint`.
- **Active nav:** white/surface pill, green text, subtle `primary` ring.

## Wordmark

- **SR:** Inter Black, small caps tracking, `text-clara-muted`.
- **Clara:** Fraunces bold, `text-clara-primary` (title case).

## Do / don’t

- **Do** use `accent` for links and focus, primary green for main actions and wordmark “Clara”.
- **Don’t** introduce extra brand fonts beyond Inter + Fraunces without updating this spec.
